org.jruyi.common

Class BiListNode<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jruyi.common.BiListNode<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the element
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, ICloseable

    public final class BiListNode<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICloseable
    A node that contains 2 references to point to previous node and next node respectively, and a reference to hold a data element. It is used to form a doubly linked list.

    This class has a thread local cache mechanism for node instances.
